org.jivesoftware.smackx.pubsub

Enum EventElementType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EventElementType>
      • org.jivesoftware.smackx.pubsub.EventElementType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<EventElementType>

    public enum EventElementType
extends Enum<EventElementType>
    This enumeration defines the possible event types that are supported within pubsub event messages.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constant and Description

      items

      purge
      All items have been purged from a node
      subscription
